{{作品名稱|name=''The Wolf of Wall Street''|hk=華爾街狼人|tw=華爾街之狼|equiv-cn=tw}}是[[马丁·斯科塞斯|马丁·斯科塞斯]]执导的2013年美国[[传记片|传记]][[黑色幽默|黑色喜剧片]]，剧本由[[泰倫斯·溫特|泰倫斯·溫特]]根据[[乔丹·贝尔福特|乔丹·贝尔福特]][[華爾街之狼_(回憶錄)|同名回忆录]]改编<ref name="Candle">{{cite news | url = https://variety.com/2013/scene/awards/terence-winter-leo-brave-enough-for-candle-scene-in-wolf-of-wall-street-1200973258/ | title = Terence Winter: Leo 'Brave Enough' for Candle Scene in 'Wolf of Wall Street' | work = [[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | publisher = Penske Media Corporation | date = 2013-12-18 | accessdate = 2021-07-03 | last = Morfoot | first = Addie | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210225173329/https://variety.com/2013/scene/awards/terence-winter-leo-brave-enough-for-candle-scene-in-wolf-of-wall-street-1200973258/ | archive-date = 2021-02-25 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥|莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥]]领衔饰演20世纪90年代在[[华尔街|华尔街]]大肆参与[[证券欺诈|证券欺诈]]和[[洗錢|洗錢]]的纽约股票经纪人贝尔福特<ref>{{cite news | archive-date = 2021-04-18 | dead-url = no | accessdate = 2021-07-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210418084131/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/jordan-belfort-real-wolf-wall-street-and-men-who-brought-him-down-9047015.html | date = 2014-01-12 | last = Harding | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/jordan-belfort-real-wolf-wall-street-and-men-who-brought-him-down-9047015.html | title = Jordan Belfort: The real Wolf of Wall Street and the men who brought him down | work = [[獨立報|The Independent]] | publisher = Independent Print Limited | first = Nick }}</ref>，其他主要演员包括[[喬納·希爾|喬納·希爾]]、[[瑪歌·羅比|瑪歌·羅比]]、[[凱爾·錢德勒|凱爾·錢德勒]]<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/reviews/wolf-wall-street-film-review-scorsese-s-film-about-rogue-trader-jordan-belfort-money-9065519.html | title = The Wolf of Wall Street, review: Scorsese's film on rogue trader Jordan Belfort is on the money | work = The Independent | publisher = Independent Print Limited | date = 2014-01-16 | accessdate = 2021-07-03 | last = MacNab | first = Geoffrey | archive-date = 2020-07-29 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200729102922/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/reviews/the-wolf-of-wall-street-film-review-scorseses-film-about-rogue-trader-jordan-belfort-is-on-the-money-9065519.html }}</ref>。

影片2013年12月17日在纽约首映<ref name="Candle" />，再经[[派拉蒙影業|派拉蒙影業]]策划圣诞节当天在北美洲和法国全面上映，最终以一亿美元预算取得超3.92亿美元全球票房<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl3447424513/ | title = The Wolf of Wall Street (2013) | publisher = [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]. IMDb | accessdate = 2021-07-03 | archive-date = 2021-05-04 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210504060527/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl3447424513/ }}</ref>，创下斯科塞斯导演作品新纪录<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/people/chart/?id=martinscorsese.htm | title = Martin Scorsese Movie Box Office Results | publisher = Box Office Mojo. [[亞馬遜公司|Amazon.com]] | accessdate = 2015-09-05 | archive-date = 2015-09-05 | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150905231721/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/people/chart/?id=martinscorsese.htm }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/general-news/wolf-wall-street-is-martin-679314/ | title = 'Wolf of Wall Street' Is Martin Scorsese's Top-Grossing Film | work = [[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]] | publisher = [[普羅米修斯環球媒體|Prometheus Global Media]] | date = 2014-02-11 | accessdate = 2021-07-03 | last = McClintock | first = Pamela | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210526100518/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/general-news/wolf-wall-street-is-martin-679314/ | archive-date = 2021-05-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 剧情 ==
1987年，在危机四伏的投资界，25岁的[[乔丹·贝尔福特|乔丹·贝尔福特]]（[[莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥|莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥]]饰）进入[[罗斯柴尔德|罗斯柴尔德]]公司，从接线员做起，在高级经纪人马克（[[马修·麦康纳|马修·麦康纳]]饰）指点下，进入了股票经纪人这个充满毒品和欲望的世界，半年后，在他第一次正式成为股票经纪人的第一天，便遇到了“[[1987年黑色星期一|黑色星期一]]”，乔丹转投靠贩卖“便士股票”的小公司，凭借巧舌如簧获得了巨大利润，之后与邻居唐尼（[[乔纳·希尔|乔纳·希尔]]饰）和一班朋友另立门户，创立了史崔顿·奥克蒙公司，他们游走在灰色地带并获利颇丰，获称“华尔街之狼”，然而，[[联邦调查局|FBI]]却已经开始留意他，最终因为卷入[[华尔街|华尔街]]一宗臭名昭著的证券诈骗案而受到[[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]的刑事调查，最后因其有立功表现而被判三年监禁，出狱后乔丹当上了股票经理培训人。

